{"tid":281422,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）倉鼠疑似有皮膚病，求好獸醫","createTime":"2017-06-12T16:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T11:29:23.000Z","uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1a115ad6b7c5f777ee1fc478fbfb819a50c643","tid":281422,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻鼠鼠2歲喇<br />\n近排發現佢甩毛，網上話老都會甩毛，所以冇為意<br />\no岩o岩見到右邊肋骨個位有抓痕，而且無乜毛<br />\n我估係皮膚病<br />\n<br />\n急求好o既倉鼠獸醫，希望聽日睇得成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3e9e52343c216a6ad31ef0431f4b40b734df08ad","tid":281422,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c1494724395b43873c22fa74de13a8a6849dd1","tid":281422,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"住邊"},{"pid":"c4676cbaee6f0c2f25c0cc9a84bbf862129ae29d","tid":281422,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住邊</blockquote><br />\n堅離地城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5785c643f4e2fba0f488edc616a7e0e0d8c9a678","tid":281422,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"Q"},{"pid":"041fa31548da068480cd738221ffa5d7869cfce1","tid":281422,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:42:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77251e04b2432a40fc24db21bdfd471e2d95bc12","tid":281422,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T04:5